<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/63000270/2025-26/syllabus> a ns1:Syllabus ;
    ns1:hasItem <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/63000270/2025-26/syllabus/0>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/63000270/2025-26/syllabus/1>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/63000270/2025-26/syllabus/2>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/63000270/2025-26/syllabus/3>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/63000270/2025-26/syllabus/4>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/63000270/2025-26/syllabus/5>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/63000270/2025-26/syllabus/6> .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/63000270/2025-26/syllabus/0> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 0 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "1. Geological and metallogenetic framework of a deposit: stratigraphy and structure. Geological controls. Structural analysis and geometry of mineral deposits. Practical application. Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/63000270/2025-26/syllabus/1> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 1 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "2. Mining exploration methods and their specific application. An example: Geochemical exploration and its phases. Application to Red Beds. Practical realization and analysis of the results. Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/63000270/2025-26/syllabus/2> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 2 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "3. Economics of exploration. Results and economic strategies associated with decisions. The risks, their formulation and analysis. Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/63000270/2025-26/syllabus/3> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 3 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "4. Exploration: technology, economy, control and operations with cores and samples. Strategies in its distribution. Application.Tipología y clasificación de yacimientos metálicos. Diversos criterios y tipos de clasificación. Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/63000270/2025-26/syllabus/4> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 4 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "5. Remote Sensing Techniques Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/63000270/2025-26/syllabus/5> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 5 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "6. The exploration within the life cycle of a mining project. Phases and competences. International codes for the preparation of mineral resources and reserves reports. Application to previous cases. Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/63000270/2025-26/syllabus/6> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 6 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "7. Resource evaluation. Cut-off grade calculation. Methodology and application of the valuation of mineral deposits. Application to a stratoligated copper deposit. Sin subniveles"@es .

